# Hello 👋 we are Odigos

### About Us

<span style="display: flex; align-items: center;">🖥️ We're an open-source distributed tracing solution <img src="https://img.shields.io/badge/Odigos-111?logo=data:image/svg+xml;base64," /></span>
<span style="display: flex; align-items: center;">🔭 We make use of <img src="https://img.shields.io/badge/OpenTelemetry-111?logo=data:image/svg+xml;base64," />, and contribute to them too</span>
<span style="display: flex; align-items: center;">🌱 We leverage <img src="https://img.shields.io/badge/eBPF-111?logo=data:image/png;base64," /> to collect the telemetry data</span>
<span style="display: flex; align-items: center;">🧠 Zero-code implementation</span>
